\Bbb E(X)=\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}\Bbb E(X_k)=\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}\left(\frac{N}{m-k}+1\right)=N\sum_{k=1}^m\frac1k+m=NH_m+m\;,
